        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焙茗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晴雯姑娘，逐出园去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉拭泪，搓手。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有这等事么？呀吓不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说逐出小晴雯，\n好似钢刀刺我心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晴雯姐姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "无限心领痛冤沉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，焙茗，不知晴雯被逐，究竟为了何事，现在何处，你可知道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "恼恨情天何太狠、焙茗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，二爷，晴雯姑娘，乃是园中最矫激，有气节的女儿，此番被逐，定是被\n那姐妹们，谗诉所中，一个逐令一下，刻不容留，就回家去了。啊，啊，啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，你与我悄悄备马，由便门出园，速去速去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焙茗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焙茗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，晴雯姐姐呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "焙茗→贾宝玉",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
          "edge": "贾宝玉→焙茗",
          "turns": 4
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
