    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "五儿",
        "晴雯",
        "晴雯嫂嫂",
        "焙茗",
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯嫂嫂扶晴雯病装同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "反二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一日别离一日心，\n病魂犹绕大观园。\n“妖狐”二字痛冤沉。\n再不能悄听潇湘琴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝玉呵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "反二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "反二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "枉费了你一段护花心，\n要想见除非是这梦里贞魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯嫂嫂推晴雯伏病床，晴雯气郁。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯嫂嫂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼，哼，不得了，姑娘，你不要装斯文了。你自己想想，当日在大观中，何等\n尊贵，哪一个高攀得上？你多少年儿，从不到娘门上。瞧一瞧你心上的人，又\n是什么姑娘哩，少爷哩，全不把我们放在眼里，我们常说，贵人是不蹈贱地的\n了，不料想今日，你还认得家。常言说得好，出了娘家门，还有姨家门，凭姑\n娘有这个模样儿，宅门上买姨娘娘的，怕买不到手啦，哭什么，瞧好的啵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯气心痛。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯嫂嫂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别撒娇了，我不喜欢那个样儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你你嫂嫂不羞，敢在我面前来，胡言乱语，还不与我快走出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯嫂嫂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走可别叫我，我看谁来服侍你，咱斗牌去，阿弥陀佛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯嫂嫂下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，天哪天那，想俺晴雯，落得这样地步，不如死了罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯昏去。贾宝玉、焙茗同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "马上伤情魂欲断，\n可怜一步一啼痕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焙茗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上前扣门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焙茗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷，门正开着，快快进去罢，免得外人瞧见，传进府去，小子耽待不起。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焙茗下，贾宝玉入门，拥晴雯。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐醒来。姐姐醒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯见贾宝玉，诧异，双手搓眼细看，欲起不能。贾宝玉扶晴雯起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我因闻知你被逐，故而急急赶来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯惊异。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我敢是做梦呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明明是我，何言做梦？\n（晴雯指案上茶壶，贾宝玉斟茶，看，作恶劣。晴雯招手，贾宝玉送茶就晴雯，晴雯举碗抚贾宝玉肩，饮茶。\n贾宝玉作暗暗下泪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "奴只道俺与你此生两参商，\n忽相见又寸断肝肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫奴好喜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜从何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "喜只喜多情公子重相见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫奴好恨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨从何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "恨只恨数年来，朝朝暮暮时时刻刻，都只为，爱惜声名，辜负鸳鸯帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯咬折手指甲纳贾宝玉荷包内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "奴只把这全腔心血交付你，\n再相见惟有是梦里高唐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯换衣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "生同室死同穴只有这件旧衣裳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，姐姐，被逐出园，因何而起？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯气急。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢，你问我这出园吗？咳，你乃好糊涂，贾二爷，呦，呦，呦，呦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（仙女暗上，晴雯嫂嫂、焙茗同上，作掩。贾宝玉作惊慌闪躲。晴雯气绝，仙女暗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯嫂嫂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，小宝贝人一市，诳狗咬利空，怪不得我……死去活来，今天大好运气，\n不料想这阵，到我怀里来了，我看宝贝，你往哪里跑。⑴"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯嫂嫂与贾宝玉扭扯，五儿上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "五儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晴雯姑娘，可好些了？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯嫂嫂惊，出迎。贾宝玉逃脱，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯嫂嫂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们姑娘好些了，你要他，随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
