    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（晴雯宫装手执姑子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃晴雯灵魂是也。警幻仙姑怜俺玉洁冰霜，无罪被逐。封俺为芙蓉花神，今\n有神瑛使者，情缘未了，撰成芙蓉诔文，在大观园中，池边相招。你看今宵，\n月白风清，不免消遣则个前去。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "晴雯",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情丝不断死犹生，赚煞天离离恨人。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
